Notes on Rails spec files
======

How the files should be oriented.

	File hierarchy

	File
	 |
	 |---lib--->(implementation file/Class file)
	 |
	 |---spec--->lib--->(spec file)


>In order to get the spec implementation working, run `sudo gem install rspec` at the top level folder. Next you must type `rspec --init` to get the spec_helper.rb file.
>>To run the spec files, use the command `rspec` at the top level folder, or you can specify the location directory explicitly by `rspec <filename>`

---------------------------------------------------

Check the code for more in-depth examples.
